channel.title: Auxy songs that get stuck in your head?
channel.description:
For me right now it's Intrepid's "The Calling," but DeCruz's Klap gets in my head a lot as well.
What about you guys?

item.title: Auxy songs that get stuck in your head?
item.dc:creator: akabillposters
item.description:
Not wishing to sound egotistic, but my own stuff gets stuck in my head.
Recently, I’ve been writing stuff that has more song-like structures with ‘hooks’, etc…

I’m playing it over and over because…

  1. I’m enjoying it and …
  2. I’m always reviewing each piece with possible changes in mind – what’s working, what’s not, are the sounds right, are the levels good, where could I take it if I develop it further, …
